  "title": "Assistant Outlet Manager",
  "description": "<h1><strong>🥐 Passion Is Our Main Ingredient🥐</strong></h1><p><strong>Baker & Cook Singapore </strong>- Singapore’s only true artisan bakery & foodstore is hiring!</p><h3>💰 <strong>** Attractive Sign-on Bonus**</strong>💰</h3><p>✅ Singaporean* | Singapore PR* | PLOC</p><p>✅ 6-days work week</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>🍕 Outlets: Asian Civilizations Museum </strong>| <strong>Café Carrera by Baker & Cook (Guoco Midtown) | Café Carrera by Baker & Cook (Jewel) | Chip Bee Garden | Dairy Farm | Dempsey | Eng Kong Park | Hillcrest | Namly Place | South Bouna Vista | Serangoon Garden | Swan Lake | Sunset Way</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Assist the Store Manager to oversee operation with focus on sales management, customer satisfaction, operating expenses and shop’s profitability</li><li>Assist with rostering efficiently and cost-effectively to match business needs and sales</li><li>Supervise and train the team in accordance to the Baker & Cook DNA</li><li>Enforce and ensure compliance to Company SOPs, governmental regulations, food safety and hygiene standards within the store</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties base on operational needs</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Passionate about service and people</li><li>Preferably Diploma in Hospitality or related fields</li><li>Preferably 1 year managerial or 2 years supervisory experience in F&B – cafes/ restaurants/ similar capacity</li><li>Good team player and self-motivated</li><li>6 days work week and able to work on weekends/public holidays</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>Medical + dental benefits</li><li>Birthday vouchers</li><li>Staff discounts across brands</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested party may apply via https://forms.gle/G1q4e4nDrfW1yDmL7</p><p>** T&C applies</p>",
